{"tid":2516900,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"無良文華逼員工啪針，仲去staycation?","createTime":"2021-05-05T03:20:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T03:25:20.000Z","uid":345733,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"15ad7f44038b01375c981e6884a7be4891ab3708","tid":2516900,"uid":345733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T03:20:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQj6XQ2Ny9nWc4pdBbuv1sFyvNuaF2tziu5N2Mo6A3VUw?filename=R1sRNOJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR1sRNOJ.jpg&h=03379d43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本會接到會員反映，指文華東方酒店，以口頭方式要求餐飲部門同事需要於本周內預約接種疫苗，並提供相關資料予人事部作證明。<br />\n<br />\n拒絕接種疫苗者，必須透過任何本港註冊醫生證明不適宜接種疫苗。酒店仍然未有說明不接種疫苗而又未能提供醫生證明不適合接種疫苗的同事的後果。<br />\n<br />\n(1)文華東方酒店一向以書面方式向員工發出公告，但對<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">疫苗接種一事酒店方採用口頭方式發佈</span></span></span>，酒店藏頭露尾，利用員工的恐懼，<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">脅迫員工面對不必要的死亡風險，並害怕和迴避傳媒和公眾的質詢。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n(2)根據文華東方酒店發出的企業社會責任報告書*，酒店方承諾對員工健康與安全負責，並採取措施以保障員工生命；但疫苗接種後的死亡個案和不良反應者不斷，酒店方仍強迫員工接種，彷彿對員工生命之不顧。<br />\n<br />\n(3)酒店以人為本的品牌形象是透過員工和地方社會的連結組成，至今酒店排除品牌理念之不顧，與人和社會脫節，彷彿由溫暖細意的酒店變成冷漠寒冰的建築物，一切承諾猶如空口講白話。<br />\n<br />\n(4)貴酒店貴為國際上市公司，根據國際案例，如強迫員工，違反人民價值，由各國以自願方式轉為酒店方強迫要員工接種方式而引伸健康的問題，將帶來酒店巨額之賠償，敬請酒店三思而後行，以免觸發公關危機。<br />\n<br />\n本會促請文華東方酒店就其企業責任報告書作出回應，解釋如何在要求同事接種疫苗的情況下，保障同事享有報告書中列出之國際勞工組織公約及世界人權宣言中有關享有生命、人權、自由及人身安全的權利，以及如何確保接種疫苗不會對同事身體造成負面影響。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">本會再次重申，接種疫苗與否，本應是根據個人意願以及個人身體狀況而決定，而非受壓或脅迫下去接種。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n* 文華東方酒店的企業社會責任報告書 (參考：18,23頁)<br />\n<a href=\"http://photos.mandarinoriental.com/is/content/MandarinOriental/mandarin-oriental-sustainability-report-2019-\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotos.mandarinoriental.com%2Fis%2Fcontent%2FMandarinOriental%2Fmandarin-oriental-sustainability-report-2019-&d=qHuNkoJYq05zO%2BFPSordK732HZRMtn4xjJY4gFhUisg%3D&h=d40d9357\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://photos.mandarinoriental.com/is/content/MandarinOriental/mandarin-oriental-sustainability-report-2019-</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家唔好忘記文華東方都係撐警怡和旗下架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好一有staycation就個個仆住去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc9636ec380613fd60ce598b343c9c4c15eb208f","tid":2516900,"uid":345733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T03:20:38.000Z","msg":"推1<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7a1b619d8de196f7e1558be2d2142c2365bc886","tid":2516900,"uid":345733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T03:20:51.000Z","msg":"推2<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d0095814627ed22b2d25361acf10493baff8eab","tid":2516900,"uid":345733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T03:21:06.000Z","msg":"推3<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1078f897959bc25cd44389f5886cb8cbe22ea28","tid":2516900,"uid":37957,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T03:22:16.000Z","msg":"怡和=仁孚行=水炮車代理"},{"pid":"f2d93